---
title: Double Mumbai-Style Haloumi & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Cashews
description: This darkly rich haloumi curry is like a golden sunset. Filled to the brim with bright veggies and a sprinkling of flair from the tomato-based sauce, we think this beaming bowl will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night.
